'''Andrea Buratti''' is an [[United States|American]] [[Contract bridge|bridge]] player.

==Bridge accomplishments==

===Wins===

* [[World Transnational Open Teams Championship]] (1) 2003 <ref>[http://www.worldbridge.org/transnational-open-teams.aspx World Transational Open Teams Winners]</ref>

* [[Rosenblum Cup]] (1) 1998 <ref>[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-open-teams.aspx Rosenblum Cup Winners]</ref>

* [[Cavendish Invitational|Cavendish Invitational Pairs]] (1) 2005 <ref>[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-team-championships.aspx World Team Championship Winners]</ref>

* [[North American Bridge Championships]] (1)
